<p>The <code>pad</code> tag is a generic PAD include/processing tag.</p>

<h2>Basic Usage</h2>
<pre>{open}pad{close}
  Template content with {open}$variables{close}
{open}/pad{close}</pre>

<h2>Process with Data</h2>
<pre>{open}pad data='items'{close}
  Item: {open}$value{close}
{open}/pad{close}</pre>
{pad data='items'}
<p>Item: {$value}</p>
{/pad}

<h2>Set Variable and Use</h2>
<pre>{open}set greeting='Welcome'{close}
{open}pad{close}
  {open}$greeting{close} to PAD!
{open}/pad{close}</pre>
{set greeting='Welcome'}
{pad}
<p>{$greeting} to PAD!</p>
{/pad}

<h2>Nested PAD Processing</h2>
<pre>{open}pad{close}
  Outer content
  {open}pad{close}
    Inner content
  {open}/pad{close}
{open}/pad{close}</pre>
{pad}
<div style="border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px;">
  Outer content
  {pad}
  <div style="border:1px solid #999; padding:5px; margin:5px;">
    Inner content
  </div>
  {/pad}
</div>
{/pad}

<h2>Use Cases</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Process dynamic template content</li>
  <li>Create reusable template blocks</li>
  <li>Iterate over data with custom templates</li>
</ul>

<h2>Comparison</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Tag</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
  <tr><td>pad</td><td>Generic PAD processing</td></tr>
  <tr><td>page</td><td>Include external page files</td></tr>
  <tr><td>content</td><td>Store content for later</td></tr>
  <tr><td>get</td><td>Retrieve stored content</td></tr>
</table>
